{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"PLAN-REVIEW TRIAGE (verdict PASS; 10 advisories). Accepted: (1) add ACs asserting the ref/source DEFAULTS (ref=origin/main, source=attested); (2) add an AC confirming all three re-rooting touchpoints (gate_ops, completion.py, operations._assemble_context) consume the snapshot handle, not just the interface; (3) state the expand-contract / back-out story for changing all five gates' code-root behavior (defaults mitigate, but make it explicit); (4) specify consumer tolerance when the snapshot dir is absent/stale/being GC'd (ENOENT -> re-materialize, per S2); (5) strengthen the AC4 regression oracle: assert the attested verdict is identical regardless of the server's checked-out branch (a behavioral contract, NOT an output snapshot/change-detector); (6) clarify repo_root's role in local mode; (7) ADR cross-ref (shared with S4)."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782522697206757001,"uuid":"1fea3f9b-a6ce-482c-a0b4-56c232a14441"}